The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes it relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves semantic understanding of 3D scenes, which may make it relevant to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
